data.description: Back by popular demand! This exceptional home is making a grand return to the market, offering a second chance for you to make it yours. WHY WAIT TO BUILD, when you can have this move-in ready Stunning home Available Now!!! Over 4,260 St. Ft. Feature 5 beds, 4 full bathrooms, half bathroom on the first floor, & 3 car garage. Almost brand new & gorgeous house in the beautiful Hawkstone Community with the builder warranties. The Belmar Floor Plan By WestBay offers a combination of Luxury and Tranquility. Walking through the glass doors into this elegant place, and be impressed with the Grand Entrace vaulted ceiling in the foyer, which opens to the den/office with french doors, dining room and the split-garage entrances. The expansive quartz counter top island kitchen and extended cabinets make this areaa a perfect place for the whole family, the grand room and cafe open to the oversized lanai for seamless indoor and outdoor living. Downstairs guest Suite/Secondary Master Bedroom with walk-in closet, and full bathroom next to the room. Upstairs is the unbelievable owner’s retreat complete with huge walk-in closet and generous bath with large balcony accessed from the Master room and Loft Room. Secondary bedrooms joined with Jack and Jill bath, additional bed and bath, laundry and incredible loft room round out the upstairs. THIS HOUSE FEATURE: Quartz counter tops, ceiling fans, smart thermostats, elegant pendant lights, modern fixture lights, 3 chandeliers in the foyer, glass french doors, walk-in pantry, storage closets everywhere & more. Hawkstone is a master-planned community located in Lithia, FL. Residents enjoy the best of both worlds with resort-style amenities while staying close to top-rated Lithia schools, nature preserves, family-friendly activities, US-301, and I-75. Enjoy the pet-friendly hiking trails at the 969-acre Triple Creek Nature Preserve, less than 2 miles south or try your hand at bicycle motocross at Triple Creek BMX, 1 mile south of Hawkstone. Do not miss the opportunity to buy this brand new house under the price of the builder houses, and it's move-in ready. Don't miss out the opportunity to turn this house into your dream Home!!!
